Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.06,0:01:06.13,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,I'll save her no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.13,0:01:11.37,Helvetica,,0,0,3,,{\fs22}If I can't even do that much, what kind of master am I? What's the point of alchemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.37,0:01:12.77,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,No matter what?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.77,0:01:13.94,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,No matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.80,0:01:19.91,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Then I have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.41,0:01:22.91,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Sure, we may be kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.91,0:01:30.65,Helvetica,,0,0,3,,{\fs22}But someday we'll grow up. Armony isn't like that.\NThe present is all she has!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.65,0:01:34.42,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,I always knew a day like this would come.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.42,0:01:39.63,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,2080)}Get out of my way!
